title: Snow White and the 7 Dwarfs Greek Audio-Metaglotismeno (1937)
description:
Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs-H xionath kai oi 7 nanoi Greek Audio Metaglotismeno DVDRip (1953)

Apo ta wraiotera klasika paramythia twn adelfwn Gkrim H Xionath kai oi epta nanoi einai ena paradosiako Evrwpaiko paramythi. Fovismenh thn ekdikhsh ths kakias vasilissas,h Xionath, egkataleipei to palati kai vriskei katafygio se ena spitaki sto dasos, to opoio katoikeitai apo epta nanous.
Omws h vasilissa den tha papsei na thn anazhtei gia na ths kanei kako.
